snippet.title: Gravity Forge - Official Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam 👉 https://store.steampowered.com/app/2848760

Master gravity and parkour skills to slay hordes of enemies. 
As an elegant assassin, you can play solo or in co-op with friends.

Our socials are in the channel description. The launch date, and other details will be announced later. Watch this space!
